23   But He turned and said unto Peter, &quot;Get thee behind Me, Satan! Thou art an offense unto Me; for thou savorest not <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>the things that be of God</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, but those that be of men.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
